&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Taipei?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-taipei" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-taipei" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Taipei, the vibrant capital of Taiwan, is a city that effortlessly blends the modern with the traditional. Known for its stunning skyline dominated by the iconic Taipei 101, it offers a rich tapestry of culture, history, and innovation. The city&amp;rsquo;s night markets, bustling streets, and serene temples provide a unique glimpse into Taiwanese life. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re wandering through the historic lanes of Dihua Street or savoring the flavors of local street food, Taipei is a feast for the senses.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>